window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Ard and his companions are being hunted by King Martin, who has gone completely scorched earth on his own kingdom in an effort to root them out. The lovable mage finds a quiet spot in the uninhabitable wilds of Garrish to train his soul magic—only nothing ever goes quite according to Ard’s plan.</p> <p>Driven out by King Martin’s escalating mania, Ard must now go through the king to reach the goddess behind it all.</p>"; 
